                <a href="http://www.w3.org/TR/WCAG20/">WCAG 2</a>&nbsp;level AA requires a contrast ratio of at least 4.5:1 for normal text and 3:1 for large text, and a contrast ratio of at least 3:1 for graphics and user interface components (such as form input borders). Level AAA requires a contrast ratio of at least 7:1 for normal text and 4.5:1 for large text.

            </p>


            <p class="tir is-size-5-mobile m-4">
                Large text is defined as 14 point (typically 18.66px) and bold or larger, or 18 point (typically 24px) or larger.

